T1  - Consistency between Predicted and Actual Bid-Ask Quote-Revisions
AU  - JANG, HASUNG
AU  - VENKATESH, P. C.
Y1  - 1991/03/01
PY  - 1991
DA  - 1991/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1991.tb03760.x
